            "format": "markdown_easy",
            "processed": "<pre><code># Install the ultralytics package from PyPI\npip install ultralytics\n</code></pre>\n<p>You can also install ultralytics directly from the Ultralytics GitHub repository. This can be useful if you want the latest development version. Ensure you have the Git command-line tool installed, and then run:</p>\n<pre><code># Install the ultralytics package from GitHub\npip install git+https://github.com/ultralytics/ultralytics.git@main\n</code></pre>",
            "summary": "",
            "value": "```\r\n# Install the ultralytics package from PyPI\r\npip install ultralytics\r\n```\r\nYou can also install ultralytics directly from the Ultralytics GitHub repository. This can be useful if you want the latest development version. Ensure you have the Git command-line tool installed, and then run:\r\n\r\n```\r\n# Install the ultralytics package from GitHub\r\npip install git+https://github.com/ultralytics/ultralytics.git@main\r\n```"
        }
